      "description": "Clean, straightforward driver with solid bones and a strong mechanical feel. Starts up, runs, and offers a usable powertrain platform for someone wanting an affordable daily, shop truck, or weekend project. Shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but it has the kind of honest character enthusiasts appreciate\u2014simple, serviceable, and ready for continued use or a light refresh. If you want a budget-friendly vehicle with practical capability and room to make it your own, this is a compelling buy.",
